divs: sighting detailsi was leaving for work at about 9:20pm and as i went outside i noticed a bright star in the sky. upon paying closer attention to it i realized that it was moving, travelling in a nne\ne direction. at first i thought it must have been a satellite or something, but then it started moving from side to side and i was pretty sure that this wasn't a satellite. i went inside to look for a camera but when i came back out with one, it apeared to be gone, however i saw a faint moving light very far away in the east direction.
